data.description: This is a HUGE home in a very desirable Stanton Heights and yet on a quiet street, sitting away from the street on over a quarter of acre lot.  Ready for you to remodel! Needs work.   Generouse Room Sizes, spaciouse Lobby, oversized family room, large dining, a spacious additional room (could be an office/library or 5th bedroom on main), sun rooms, bay windows, plenty of natural light, spaciouse bathrooms with double sinks, closets and a posibility to install a laundry in one of them.   Large Kitchen with a dining area that could be turned into a dining, large pantry or a laundry on main. Or, maybe a small home office.   Finished basement has its own totally equipped appartment-like with its own eat-in kitchen, full bathroom, laundry area, mud/sun room and entrance to the back yard.  2 car garage and a wide concrete driveway for easy parking.   Wooded area behind the yard adds more privacy and is a part of this parcel as well.  Looks solid but needs work.
